{"tid":2115194,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Red Velvet瑟琪放送事故　「比中指嚇歪」緊急收手⋯表情包瘋傳","createTime":"2020-07-19T10:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T10:40:47.000Z","uid":74065,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e96051b9615277429b38638ec940314c9a6a59f2","tid":2115194,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:35:18.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣女團Red Velvet於7月推出小分隊組合，由IRENE與SEULGI（瑟琪）聯手出輯，帶來性感又黑暗的歌曲《Monster》，新穎的造型獲得，甫推出就獲得迴響。她們17日拿下音樂節目《Music Bank》一位殊榮，瑟琪在安可時拿起怪獸的手套準備戴上，怎料出現「放送事故」，意外在鏡頭前比出中指，嚇到她當場收手，可愛的表情包瘋傳。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5015/d5015204.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5015%2Fd5015204.jpg&h=86d850e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼Red Velvet瑟琪在戴上手套的時候，意外變成比中指，嚇到她緊急收手。（圖／翻攝自KBS Kpop）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5015/d5015205.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5015%2Fd5015205.jpg&h=4a72507f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5015/d5015203.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5015%2Fd5015203.jpg&h=8c1d59f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIRENE、瑟琪的小分隊17日奪下音樂節目《Music Bank》一位，在安可部分，兩人手上拿著許多慶祝道具，趁著氣氛開心之餘，瑟琪從IRENE手上接過一個怪獸手套物品，她將套進手套裡，卻因為手套的形狀意外比成中指，她意識到手勢不雅，瞬間在鏡頭前嚇歪、緊急收手，直到第二次嘗試才成功戴好手套，然而，這段插曲「放送事故」逗笑粉絲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5015/d5015208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5015%2Fd5015208.jpg&h=d17745ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Red Velvet推出小分隊，當天獲得一位安可時，兩人歌唱實力獲得稱讚。（圖／翻攝自KBS Kpop）<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，IRENE、瑟琪當天在安可部分秀出清唱實力，兩人歌唱水準獲得粉絲大大讚揚，尤其是IRENE雖然在隊內是擔當Rap，但歌唱部份也有一定能力，令歌迷驚艷表示「唱得真好」、「安可水準很厲害」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z3uWavE6-Q8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZ3uWavE6-Q8&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8ps4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=542717df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z3uWavE6-Q8</a><br />\n<br />\n熊熊壞女人"},{"pid":"8f28b1ca50211f177094316bc850f2bbc8d5b5ef","tid":2115194,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:38:24.000Z","msg":"哈傻仔"},{"pid":"76f5755ee81becd8f8640b4479a92745627e5104","tid":2115194,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:40:19.000Z","msg":"會唔會入廁所打冷震"},{"pid":"fa289e0582ac147e2349d3b2e5d50a60d5bd2cd5","tid":2115194,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:40:47.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}